data.description: Come enjoy one level living in this spacious ranch home on large corner lot in small town Vernonia. Built in 2001, this 1704 square foot home features three bedrooms, two bathrooms and plenty of room in the living areas of the dining room, family room, living room and kitchen. Covered back patio with partially fenced back yard for entertaining as well as plenty of parking and concrete pad for RV, two electrical RV hookups.  Outside shed and storage.  Newer heat pump, gas furnace, gas tankless water heater to help cut utility costs.  Wired for whole house generator is a nice touch for on demand electricity at a flip of a switch.  Bring your updates and finishing touches to make it your own!
